      <title>淡水河谷預計將在上半年就馬裡亞納大壩賠償達成最終協議</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/vale-expects-reach-final-agreement-mariana-dam-reparations-first-half-year-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[淡水河谷礦業公司週三在聲明中告訴路透社，該公司預計將在今年上半年年底前與當局就薩馬科尾礦壩倒塌的賠償問題達成最終協議。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/vale-expects-reach-final-agreement-mariana-dam-reparations-first-half-year-2024-04-25/</guid>
