      <title>葡萄牙民主50週年：數千人紀念康乃馨革命</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/portugals-democracy-turns-50-thousands-commemorate-carnation-revolution-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週四，數千人預計將走上街頭慶祝葡萄牙「康乃馨革命」50週年，這場革命推翻了歐洲最長的法西斯獨裁統治，迎來了民主。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/portugals-democracy-turns-50-thousands-commemorate-carnation-revolution-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 00:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
